    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an action, you slam the Tonitrus to the ground and unleash a wave of chakra in a X- foot long, 5-foot wide line (X = 10 x proficiency).</p><p>Select a damage type listed below.</p><p>Each hostile creature within range must make a Dexterity saving throw.</p><p>On a failed save, creatures take twice your proficiency bonus in your chosen damage type and gain 1 rank of a condition associated with your chosen damage type until the end of their next turn, or half damage and no effects on a pass.</p><p>When you use this tool, you can spend increments of 5 chakra to increase the width by 5 feet (up to 15ft total).</p><p>(Earth =Bruised, Wind=Bleeding, Fire=Burned, Water=Chilled, Lightning=Shocked, Force=Dazed)</p>",
